title: Play 7
overview: Violet Starr, Scarlett Alexis & Gal Ritchie are living that life: lazy mornings, lavish houses and lacy lingerie. To add to the luxury, Violet and Gal are going to teach Scarlett a new L word. Cookie & Scarlett Alexis, Octavia Red & Rissa May and Kenna James & Dylan Moore are all here frolicking in each other's folds. Flirtatious scenarios, fun settings and phenomenal girl-on-girl action.
